<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4068357>
    dc:description "Fig. 1. Habitus photographs of Malagasy species of Bidessus Sharp, 1882. A. B. apicidens Bistr̂m & Sanfilippo, 1986, ♀, paratype, http://id.luomus.fi/GL.8408 (FMNH). B. B. cf. ceratus Guignot, 1941, http://id.luomus.fi/GC.2001 (FMNH). C. B. anjozorobe sp. nov., paratype (NHRS-JLKB000025034). D. B. cf. nero Gschwendtner, 1933 (NHRS-JLKB000025032)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4068357/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4068359>
    dc:description "Fig. 2. Habitus photographs of Malagasy species of Bidessus Sharp, 1882. A. B. nesioticus Guignot, 1956 (NHRS-JLKB000025031). B. B. perexiguus Kolbe, 1883 (NHRS-JLKB000025029). C. B. longistriga Régimbart, 1895 (NHRS-JLKB000025028)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4068359/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

